{"tid":2337742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Dominion高層入稟控特朗普團隊及傳媒等舞弊指控誹謗","createTime":"2020-12-23T13:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T14:58:34.000Z","uid":75656,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"78be205e2c02416d2f2fd8102e25a1f55a86d438","tid":2337742,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:31:13.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普在大選後指控科企Dominion開發的點票軟件涉及舞弊，遭人藉此竄改點票結果，多間保守派傳媒亦有類似指控。Dominion產品策略及保安總監庫默（Eric Coomer）周二入稟法院，控告特朗普競選團隊、其兩名私人律師，以及保守派傳媒和相關人士，指它們在毫無證據下，散播選舉受操縱錯誤指控，行為屬於誹謗。特朗普一方暫未回應。<br />\n<br />\n庫默向丹佛區域法院提交入稟狀，被告包括特朗普競選團隊、特朗普私人律師朱利亞尼（Rudy Giuliani）及鮑威爾（Sidney Powell）、保守派時事評論員馬爾金（Michelle Malkin）、保守派人士奧爾特曼（Joseph Oltmann）、右翼電視台Newsmax及「一個美國新聞網絡」（One America News Network），還有網站Gateway Pundit，指它們毫無根據地指控庫默是「舞弊陰謀」的中心人物，並製造及散播宣稱Dominion操控點票機器，以有利拜登選情的失實論述，造成嚴重後果。<br />\n<br />\n庫默表示，被人認定參與選舉舞弊，令他成為公眾人物，但他只想保留私隱、生活恢復正常，形容事件使他留下陰影，警告美國正處於選舉暴力的邊緣。庫默質疑一些指控涉及政治及財政動機，決定訴諸法律程序，又指法院早前已解開2020年總統選舉的真相。入稟狀同時指，被告的行為已侵犯庫默的私穩和安全，亦損害其名譽。<br />\n<br />\nDominion近日聯同另一計票軟件開發商Smartmatic揚言以法律手段反擊舞弊指控，霍士新聞台和Newsmax已發出指示，禁止主持人在節目上提起涉及選舉舞弊的相關指控。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201223/XD6WZYCHERGJ3HFVHU7VNKBOM4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201223%2FXD6WZYCHERGJ3HFVHU7VNKBOM4%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=ba3d221b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201223%2FXD6WZYCHERGJ3HFVHU7VNKBOM4%2F&h=508ff77a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201223/XD6WZYCHERGJ3HFVHU7VNKBOM4/</a>"},{"pid":"006b960fa451a1241da0267abc8c8977179b046c","tid":2337742,"uid":137160,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"竟然咁撚大膽 聽朝侵就eo2018 拉人封艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05492e0f8328695e1a7550623fdf838b8c9b0dd","tid":2337742,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img1.gtimg.com/ent/pics/hv1/124/229/1815/118078894.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gtimg.com%2Fent%2Fpics%2Fhv1%2F124%2F229%2F1815%2F118078894.png&h=2b3ae1bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vthumb.ykimg.com/054101015DA064798B747593BEE0554E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvthumb.ykimg.com%2F054101015DA064798B747593BEE0554E&h=8ff78076&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61317ba0b4ad17161a734d5214e542b01d9e0bf2","tid":2337742,"uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:46:27.000Z","msg":"又係用司法階段去減弱傳媒報導Dominion系統 , 目的都係拖時間到 1月20 , 之後就撤控不了了之"},{"pid":"871c31cbf45d2131ef1d09cc12966f9b7beec7c7","tid":2337742,"uid":308915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"同民主黨班友一樣 賊喊捉賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe547a229d7893d1a425764b5fa3683412e776e0","tid":2337742,"uid":52658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:57:29.000Z","msg":"賊喊捉賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc90b9000648c85781fbfa6b4f60c567a487715","tid":2337742,"uid":54125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"港共咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}